Different banks offer significantly different FD interest rates — the difference between SBI (6.5%) and a small finance bank (8.5%) for the same 3-year FD can translate into several thousand rupees on a ₹10 lakh deposit. This calculator computes the maturity value at multiple interest rates simultaneously so you can compare and choose the best option.
